--- 
title  : OpenDSL
suite  : rubyworks
summary: The ultimate DSL
contact: trans <transfire@gmail.com>
authors: Thomas Sawyer
license: MIT
created: 2009-07-18

description:
  OpenDSL is the ultimate DSL system. It
  marries the concept of duck-typing with
  Ruby's metaprogramming capabilities and
  mixin system to create a remarkably simple
  but incredibly powerful DSL framework.

resources:
  homepage    : http://rubyworks.github.com/opendsl
  development : http://github.com/rubyworks/opendsl
  repository  : git://github.com/rubyworks/opendsl.git

